main event: Witnesses observed a multi-colored, 'X' shaped object moving slowly across the sky for approximately 20 minutes.
interesting points: The object emitted a humming sound during the sighting., The sighting lasted from around 2 to 5 minutes but the object was visible for almost 20 minutes., The object was observed by several witnesses, including a caretaker., The sighting was reported during a time when no balloons or planes were released or flying in the area., There is speculation it could have been a star of unusual brightness and size.
witness description: a caretaker at Shady Lanes Rest Home
